# 5. 動画撮影！

Saki: This is it...!
Saki: The day when Leo/need shoots its very first video has finally arrived!
Rin: <Yay♪>
MEIKO: <Hehe. This should be fun. Especially considering how much you girls practiced for this day.>
Rin: <Ichi, you gotta sing the best you possibly can today.>
Ichika: Yawn... Oh, um... Yeah...
Miku: <Did you not get much sleep last night, Ichika...?>
Luka: <Maybe it's because of all the practice you've been doing.>
Ichika: No, I'm just... Yes, I'm a little tired from practicing, but there's another reason...
Saki: Oh, really?! Did you stay up late playing video games or something?!
Shiho: She's not you, Saki.
Saki: I don't stay up super late playing video games... That much...! Even if I do it sometimes with movies and manga!
Len: <Don't those all fall into one category?>
Honami: Are you sure you're okay, Ichika? Do you feel tired because...?
Ichika: No, I'm okay. There's no need to worry.
Ichika: I'm actually almost finished with it. I just need to make some final adjustments.
Honami: ...! Really?! That's wonderful...!
Ichika: But choosing just one is taking more time than I initially expected. I've been trying to remember what Kanade said the other day, but...
Honami: It's okay to give something important a lot of thought. In any case, Ichika, I'll be looking forward to hearing your song.
Saki: Oh, what are you two talking about?
Ichika: Uhh... N-Nothing!
Ichika: Anyway, let's start shooting since we've asked Miku and the others to come over from SEKAI.
Honami: R-Right. I brought a few different smartphone tripods with me today. I'm hoping that they'll allow us to take a nice video.
KAITO: <Oh, I haven't seen one of those before...>
Saki: I was wondering why you were carrying so much stuff today, Hona! It was all stuff for our shoot!
Saki: But do we really need all these tripods...? We're only using one camera, right?
Honami: No, it'll be difficult for us to make a dynamic video with just one camera. Using several will give us shots from different angles, which we can stitch together for our music video.
Honami: So, would it be okay if I borrowed your phones...?
Shiho: Sure, I don't mind...
Saki: You're always super reliable, Hona, but you seem like you're really on your game today!
Honami: Th-Thank you, but this is nothing special, really!
Honami: But I want to do what I can since this video is going to help determine Leo/need's future...
Ichika: Honami...
Saki: Alright, let's take a really awesome video! Get ready! We're on standby♪
Ichika: Wh-Whoa...
Shiho: Wait, Saki, don't push...
Ichika: Okay, we're in position now...
Saki: How do we look? Are we all in the frame?
Miku: <No problems with this camera.>
Rin: <Same here!>
MEIKO: <Ours looks good too. I think you girls can start shooting.>
Ichika: Alright, then... Should we start playing?
Honami: O-Okay...
Saki: I'm getting nervous... And not like when we're about to do a show either...
Shiho: To be fair, we're not trying to do this in one take. We can always shoot again if we don't like what we see. So, let's just give it a try.
Ichika: Right... Then, let's just try to relax and play the way we practiced...
Honami: Okay, I'll count us in. One, two, three, four...
Ichika: ♪————
Ichika: (I don't understand. We all seem to be playing just fine...)
Ichika: (But something feels different...)
Rin: <Hmmmm...?>
Luka: <We've done quite a few takes already... But something does seem strange here...>
Len: <Yeah... And it's not like they have been playing bad...>
Rin: <But it's like... I dunno how to describe it!!!>
KAITO: <They're not playing with enough power...>
Rin: <Yeah, that! Nice one, KAITO!>
Miku: <They're all clearly playing like they mean it... But they're not quite fully committed.>
Ichika: ...
Shiho: Wanna stop for a sec...?
Saki: I knew it. We're missing our usual power.
Honami: I kept trying to refocus myself after each take, but I can't seem to play the way I do during shows...
Ichika: The way we play during shows...
Ichika: Yeah... We really gave it everything we had that time... It almost felt like each note shined, you know...?
Saki: Oh, I totally know what you mean! Before the show, the tension felt kinda different compared to normal...
Saki: And things were completely different during it! I could hear the audience talking and stuff like always, but I was way more focused on the show itself...
Ichika: Yeah, it'd make for a great video if we could play like that.
Shiho: That's easier said than done... We were able to play that way because of the crowd and the atmosphere.
KAITO: <Then, why not try to recreate that...?>
Saki: Wait, what do you mean...?
Len: <Oh, I think I get what he means. I doubt you girls have a spare live house just lying around...>
Len: <But what if you had some spectators? We can be your crowd!>
Ichika: Does that mean...?
Rin: <Oh, I get it!>
Rin: <We get to have Leo/need play a special concert just for us☆>
Honami: A special show just for you...?!
Saki: Yeah, that could actually work...!
Shiho: I agree. It'll help to have a visible crowd that we want to have hear our song.
Ichika: We'll do everything we can to give you guys the best performance possible, Miku...
Miku: <Hehe. Let's see what you can do.>
Shiho: Okay, it's time for Leo/need's special show...
Shiho: Let's go.
Ichika: Yeah!
